          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Assume that we deal with p-p scattering of the",
                "impinging proton by an individual proton in the",
                "lithium nucleus. After the collision, the two protons",
                "escape without suffering any other collision;",
                "otherwise they would not be detected by the counter",
                "arrangement used. The protons in the lithium nucleus,",
                "however, are not at rest and in applying the",
                "conservation of energy and momentum to the system we",
                "shall take into account, by some admittedly crude",
                "assumptions, the internal motion of the protons and",
                "their binding energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
